  "remarks": "\nJSC SCIENTIFIC RESEARCH INSTITUTE ‘SOLITON’ is an \"involved person\" under the Russian (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 because it is or has been involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia by carrying on business in a sector of strategic significance to the Government of Russia, namely the Russian defence sector. \n",
